node.text:
Your language to the universe is frequency! The word consciousness is thrown about so casually that it’s easy to lose sight of what it means, even more so when it is defined as being “awakened.” Awakened consciousness is a state of being aware that you are aware. It is a realization that you are the watcher, the witness within you—not the analyzer, not the thinker, not even the meditator, but that which is the impartial witness of every aspect of your being and doing. 

Follow @MichaelbBeckwith for more!

node.title: Follow @MichaelbBeckwith for more wisdom on the law of attraction!✨

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'HOW FOOLISH OF YOU, TO HAVE SEEN THE BAD AND YET FAIL TO BE DEEPLY GRATEFUL FOR THE GOOD? FAIRYSFORUM'.
Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'SOMETIMES YOU WANT THINGS TO WORK OUT so BADLY THEN SUDDENLY YOU JUST DON'T. Dau Voire SOnO'.
Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5 ways to forgive someone who didn't apologize by Najwa Zebian'.
Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5 ways to forgive someone who didn't apologize by Najwa Zebian'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1. Stand in your truth You know what you went through. You don't need their admission or validation of what happened. -Najwa Zebian'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2. Don't say "it's okay" when it's not. Allow yourself to fully feel the pain of what they did. Their inability to apologize doesn't mean that it was okay. You decide that. -Najwa Zebian'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3. Don't keep the door open to those who consistently hurt you. Part of holding them accountable is about you drawing boundaries and taking away their access to you. -Najwa Zebian'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Don't allow them to gaslight you into believing that it's all in your head or you're too sensitive. If it hurts, it hurts Someone who cares about you validates your feelings without shaming you. -Najwa Zebian'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5. Understand that forgiving them doesn't depend on their apology. Forgiving them means that their actions don't control you anymore. It means that you see them as humans who've treated you from their own level of maturityand awareness. Your ability to see that helps you take away from their power over you. -Najwa Zebian'.
Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'YOU CAN'T TOUCH LOVE WITH DIRTY HANDS AND WAIT FOR A MIRACLE. Malanda Jean- Claude THE WOnO'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on July 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I DON'T THINK SHE IS PERFECT. SHE 19 FLAWED AND BROKEN LIKE THE REST OF US. BUT THE PIECES SHE HAS LEFT OF HER HEART MATCH THE PIECES MISSING FRom MINE. SHE IS NOT PERFECT BUT SHE DOES MAKE ME WHOLE. -BLAKE AUDEN'.
